title: acar_ketimun
---

= Ingredients

@cucumber{1}
@red onion{1}
@red pepper{1}(without seeds)
@vinegar{6%tbsp}
@water{250%ml}
@sugar{1%tbsp}
@salt{0.5%tbsp}

= Instructions

Cut @red onion{1} into thin rings. Cut @cucumber{1} into thin slices.

Cook @vinegar{6%tbsp}, @salt{0.5%tbsp}, @sugar{1%tbsp} and @red pepper{1}(without seeds) together and let it cool down.

Put @cucumber{1} and @red onion{1} in a #jar{} and add the liquid.

